Package: powerNMA
Title: Comprehensive Network Meta-Analysis Suite with Time-Varying Methods
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("NMA", "Research Group", email = "research@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "AI", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: A comprehensive framework for network meta-analysis combining time-varying
    methods (RMST and milestone survival) with advanced NMA techniques including
    transportability weighting, Bayesian inference, meta-regression with splines,
    publication bias assessment, sensitivity analyses, and machine learning for
    heterogeneity exploration. Features an integrated Shiny dashboard and extensive
    development tools.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
